<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>About Us | Aspire Packaging</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fdfdfd;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #8b0000;
      color: white;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #8b0000;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section p {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      text-align: center;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #8b0000;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    footer {
      background: #222;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>About Aspire Packaging</h1>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      Aspire Packaging is a leading manufacturer and distributor of packaging machinery, delivering innovation and quality to customers across industries. With a strong foundation of technical expertise and over a decade of industry experience, we are committed to helping businesses optimize their packaging processes.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Our Trusted Partners</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=Logo" alt="Partner 1">
        <h3>Hualian Machinery</h3>
        <p>Our global OEM partner for coding, sealing, and strapping machines.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=Logo" alt="Partner 2">
        <h3>PAC Technologies</h3>
        <p>Collaborating on sustainable packaging solutions and automation systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=Logo" alt="Partner 3">
        <h3>Flexo Systems</h3>
        <p>Strategic partner for flexographic printing and labeling machinery.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Our Core Team</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=CEO" alt="CEO">
        <h3>Rajesh Verma</h3>
        <p>Founder & CEO</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=CTO" alt="CTO">
        <h3>Sneha Mehta</h3>
        <p>Chief Technology Officer</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=COO" alt="COO">
        <h3>Abhishek Kumar</h3>
        <p>Operations Head</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x100.png?text=Sales" alt="Sales">
        <h3>Ritika Shah</h3>
        <p>Sales & Partnerships</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Aspire Packaging. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
